{"TopicId":139922,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.8.x] NavBallAdjustor v1.9.2 : Adjust markers scale, colors, priorities, behavior","CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-16T22:37:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-16T22:37:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:48px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003ENavBallAdjustor\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#696969;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EFor KSP 1.8.x\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDescription\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNavBallAdjustor mod allows you to adjust scale/colors/priorities for navball markers and configure collapse behavior. You can disaccustom navball to hide on Map View or force it to be afraid of the mouse cursor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHow to use\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0. Unpack ZIP to KSP game folder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Start the game and click on \u0022gear\u0022 icon on the top of NavBall. Adjust any NavBall option.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Go back to forum thread and like this post. Done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EChange NavBall markers colors instructions\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSelect the marker at the right side, prograde is selected by default, and click on color picker area on any color you want. Observe the navball, prograde marker color is changed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want to revert color - click on the left side of colored rectangle under the color picker.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo set the same color for retrograde marker click on \u0022\u0026gt;\u0022 button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EShort video demonstration\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Lv-i__j7Trw?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EPictures\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Settings_Toggle.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://s32.postimg.org/y7nra5thx/Settings_Toggle.png\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022Adjusted_Markers1.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://s32.postimg.org/hipwerugl/Adjusted_Markers1.png\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022Adjusted_Markers2.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://s32.postimg.org/mvalyj9x1/Adjusted_Markers2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOptions:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Settings_Window.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.piccy.info/i9/6a163626bb08a045da33c9de955ad092/1497209056/81607/1153389/Settings_Window.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Color_Settings_Window.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://s32.postimg.org/3vty0sd11/Color_Settings_Window.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGhost markers:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022UjC225d.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UjC225d.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/704/NavBallAdjustor\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESpaceDock\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/IDizor/NavBallAdjustor/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGitHub\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso mod is available in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESource code\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/IDizor/NavBallAdjustor\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGitHub\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ELicence\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGPLv3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EChange log\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease see the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/IDizor/NavBallAdjustor/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGitHub releases page\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink ipsAttachLink_right\u0022 href=\u0022https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick\u0026amp;hosted_button_id=UB7EHSTKMHVY2\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022float:right;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022btn_donate_LG.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 style=\u0022width:92px;height:auto;\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-12-01T16:19:22Z\u0022 title=\u002212/01/2019 04:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 1, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Dizor\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MK3424","CreatedById":19932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-16T23:25:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow... if Sarbian was here.. he would have made this stock, just like he did with his ui scaler.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"White Owl","CreatedById":10849,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-16T23:53:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSlick!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow difficult would it be to add color editing for the various markers, for those of us who like alternate navball textures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T10:35:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems to be useful, I\u0027ll definitely try it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA modder\u0027s question: have you figured out a way to get rid of those silly waypoint icons on navball?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-17T10:36:04Z\u0022 title=\u002205/17/2016 10:36  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Ser\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T11:18:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222585766\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463442781\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210849\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022White Owl\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, White Owl said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSlick!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow difficult would it be to add color editing for the various markers, for those of us who like alternate navball textures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, good idea. Will investigate this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222586428\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463481319\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104207\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ser\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, Ser said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems to be useful, I\u0027ll definitely try it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA modder\u0027s question: have you figured out a way to get rid of those silly waypoint icons on navball?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean icons from left side of navball? This is not a problem, but I\u0027m okay with these icons so I did not touch them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T12:17:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222586473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463483883\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161502\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dizor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n50 minutes ago, Dizor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean icons from left side of navball? This is not a problem, but I\u0027m okay with these icons so I did not touch them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean when you accept a survey contract, go to the Map view and click \u0022Activate navigation\u0022 on a waypoint, an icon depicting a pair of feet or a notepad is displayed right on the navball showing you the direction to that waypoint. Do you know how to get rid of it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T12:31:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222586550\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463487469\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104207\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ser\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Ser said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean when you accept a survey contract, go to the Map view and click \u0022Activate navigation\u0022 on a waypoint, an icon depicting a pair of feet or a notepad is displayed right on the navball showing you the direction to that waypoint. Do you know how to get rid of it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever seen it before, but it looks to be adjustable. Will check.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T22:04:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMod is updated. Change log:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Added possibility to adjust scale for Survey Nav Waypoints.\u003Cbr\u003E\n2. Labels for inactive markers are gray now in mod settings window.\u003Cbr\u003E\n3. NavBall will not be afraid of mouse cursor when Modifier Key is pressed.\u003Cbr\u003E\n4. Fixed vessel control bug on Map View when \u0022Stock AutoHide NavBall\u0022 feature is turned off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"patrioticparadox","CreatedById":116762,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-18T07:48:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome. Gonna\u00A0check this out!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"reckless rocket","CreatedById":6244,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-18T19:40:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood one mate, cheers!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-18T22:36:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222585766\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463442781\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210849\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022White Owl\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 16.05.2016 at 2:53 AM, White Owl said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSlick!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow difficult would it be to add color editing for the various markers, for those of us who like alternate navball textures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is not difficult. But first I have to implement the color picker for this feature. Will include this in next mod update!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Enceos","CreatedById":110725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-20T12:32:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161502\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dizor\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Lovely work! Would you mind giving\u00A0some eye candy to your SpaceDock page for this mod? The markup there supports youtube vids, imgur albums etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-20T20:34:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222592354\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463747524\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Enceos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Enceos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161502\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dizor\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Lovely work! Would you mind giving\u00A0some eye candy to your SpaceDock page for this mod? The markup there supports youtube vids, imgur albums etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSure, i will update SpaceDock page once i find time for this)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-20T21:23:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161502\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dizor\u003C/a\u003E Great job on this!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAny chance of sometime taking a look at navball texture replacement as an added feature?\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSpecifically, something like this:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/63113-making-high-contrast-nav-ball/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;embedComment=959807\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Enceos","CreatedById":110725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-21T02:50:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0You don\u0027t like \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/96851-11-texturereplacer-2413-442016/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=1658372\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Etexture replacer\u003C/a\u003E?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shoe7ess","CreatedById":114974,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-21T04:05:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/135395-11-makeitsmall-12-because-sometime-you-need-stuff-to-be-smaller/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe work in some of this functionality? Or even collaborate since we don\u0027t have a working Enhanced Navball Indicator mod at the moment (mod author abandoned it).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-21T12:58:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222593717\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463799036\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Enceos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Enceos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0You don\u0027t like \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/96851-11-texturereplacer-2413-442016/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=1658372\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Etexture replacer\u003C/a\u003E?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI admit, I\u0027ve never used it... I HAVE considered it several times, however, everytime I consider all the listed functionality, the ONLY thing I would really want it for, comes down to ONLY replacing the navball texture... Which the NavBall Texture Changer mod does (did) well, and simply...\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027m a simplist, and my OCD, (and my older laptop), urges me to only use mods that are greater than like, 75% useful in functionality... lol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI took a shot at recompiling NavBall Changer, but not knowing very much about programming, I failed...\u003Cbr\u003E\nI know recently \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/75857-xevilreeperx/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002275857\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/75857-xevilreeperx/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@xEvilReeperx\u003C/a\u003E has been activley poking at some of the mods on his/her repository, but it looks like NC hasnt been touched in quite awhile... NC is one of the very first mods I install in every new KSP install... Been missing it... Would be nice to get that functionality back, without having to install, what would for me, be a very bloated mod (TextureReplacer).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-21T13:02:29Z\u0022 title=\u002205/21/2016 01:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 21, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Enceos","CreatedById":110725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-21T14:23:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222593799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463803517\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114974\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022shoe7ess\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, shoe7ess said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EMake it Small\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe work in some of this functionality? Or even collaborate since we don\u0027t have a working Enhanced Navball Indicator mod at the moment (mod author abandoned it).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/114974-shoe7ess/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022114974\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/114974-shoe7ess/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@shoe7ess\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Make it Small became stock in 1.1.2, open the settings menu in the game to see all the tweaks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Texture Replacer is not a bloated mod, it just has access to most of the ingame textures. The .dll is just 64Kb. You won\u0027t notice it in your game. I believe you never tried it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-21T14:23:53Z\u0022 title=\u002205/21/2016 02:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 21, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Enceos\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shoe7ess","CreatedById":114974,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-22T03:26:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222594227\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463840619\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Enceos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Enceos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/114974-shoe7ess/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022114974\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/114974-shoe7ess/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@shoe7ess\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Make it Small became stock in 1.1.2, open the settings menu in the game to see all the tweaks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Texture Replacer is not a bloated mod, it just has access to most of the ingame textures. The .dll is just 64Kb. You won\u0027t notice it in your game. I believe you never tried it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow, didn\u0027t even realize that. Thanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drew Kerman","CreatedById":103177,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-22T14:05:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110725-enceos/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022110725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110725-enceos/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Enceos\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0It should be noted that there are reports that TR navball texture swap is currently broken\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-22T17:50:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew version is available. Added possibility to change markers colors!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deimos Rast","CreatedById":157420,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-22T18:02:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161502\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dizor\u003C/a\u003E didn\u0027t see it mentioned, but the little button thingy stays visible when there is no navball in IVA. Love the mod though,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-22T18:08:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222593274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463779418\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 20.05.2016 at 0:23 AM, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny chance of sometime taking a look at navball texture replacement as an added feature?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis feature can be very useful, but I dont\u0027n know a way to change texture dynamically at the moment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222595975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463940135\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157420\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deimos Rast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Deimos Rast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161502\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dizor\u003C/a\u003E didn\u0027t see it mentioned, but the little button thingy stays visible when there is no navball in IVA. Love the mod though,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you. Will check and fix.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-22T18:31:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFixed and uploaded to \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/IDizor/NavBallAdjustor/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGitHub\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/704/NavBallAdjustor\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESpaceDock\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-22T22:33:38Z\u0022 title=\u002205/22/2016 10:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 22, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Dizor\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Skalou","CreatedById":133496,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-24T19:31:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nreally nice mod anyway, thank you to share it! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn other idea of suggest: include the ghost marker from the no more maintained:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/46454-10-enhanced-navball-13/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77210-ignath/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F46454-10-enhanced-navball-13%252F%2526page%253D13%2526csrfKey%253D6d225c985e17504194adc255a287d14d\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77210-ignath/\u0022 title=\u0022Go to Ignath\u0027s profile\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EIgnath:\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGhosting displays the nodes that are \u0022behind\u0022 the navball. \u00A0They appear on the navball but are \u0022ghosted\u0022 (more faded than the nodes that are not \u0022behind\u0022 the navball)\u00A0out. \u00A0It makes things much easier to see exactly where your nodes are and where they are moving while you burn. \u00A0It may make it easier for you to follow a 45 degree burn between pro and normal, as it makes it easier to see where nodes are if they\u0027re not on the visible face of the navball.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-24T19:34:25Z\u0022 title=\u002205/24/2016 07:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 24, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Skalou\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}